            <title>[CASSANDRA-9564] Backport CASSANDRA-9057 to 2.0</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-9564</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It seems that the issue described in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-9057&quot; title=&quot;index validation fails for non-indexed column&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-9057&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-9057&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; also manifests on the 2.0 branch, so we should backport the fix from 2.1.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
