                            <comment id="14577195" author="beobal" created="Mon, 8 Jun 2015 13:40:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=carlyeks&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;carlyeks&quot;&gt;carlyeks&lt;/a&gt; would you mind reviewing please? &lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="14577277" author="carlyeks" created="Mon, 8 Jun 2015 14:44:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14577518" author="beobal" created="Mon, 8 Jun 2015 17:38:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;CI unit test run look good (&lt;a href=&quot;http://cassci.datastax.com/job/beobal-9564-testall/2/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://cassci.datastax.com/job/beobal-9564-testall/2/&lt;/a&gt;) but there&apos;s an (unrelated) issue with getting a clean dtest run on 2.0 at the moment. &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=peterv&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;peterv&quot;&gt;peterv&lt;/a&gt; are you able to test the patch in the meantime?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14578403" author="peterv" created="Tue, 9 Jun 2015 06:32:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=beobal&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;beobal&quot;&gt;beobal&lt;/a&gt; I have downloaded the 2.0.15 sources and applied the patch and ran an ant build. The resulting 2.0.15-snapshot jar files copied into the lib folder of a 2.0.15 binary download(removed the 2.0.15 jars). Started this cassandra instance and ran the problematic scenario: and the result is as expected!&lt;br/&gt;
To be sure I created the pacthed build correctly I started an original 2.0.15 release to confirm the issue was still present in this version(and it was).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14578422" author="peterv" created="Tue, 9 Jun 2015 06:39:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Maybe my test should be repeated with other changes already made for the 2.0.16 release but I am not sure how to get those sources(I have used &apos;git checkout cassandra-2.0.15&apos; to apply the patch to)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14578477" author="beobal" created="Tue, 9 Jun 2015 07:26:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=peterv&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;peterv&quot;&gt;peterv&lt;/a&gt;, to grab the latest 2.0 changes (i.e. what will become 2.0.16 at some point), just checkout the head of the 2.0 branch with &lt;tt&gt;git checkout cassandra-2.0&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve committed this to the 2.0 branch in &lt;tt&gt;3ddd17b77ca39634badf62b0eaf39632d39fe008&lt;/tt&gt; and merged upwards with &lt;tt&gt;--s ours&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14578510" author="peterv" created="Tue, 9 Jun 2015 08:00:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Also with the &apos;cassandra-2.0&apos; branch it works as expected!&lt;br/&gt;
Thanks &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=beobal&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;beobal&quot;&gt;beobal&lt;/a&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
